    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), featuring the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve. This example features a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle, providing direct engagement and mechanical feedback. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration. Recent service includes a borescope inspection and IMS bearing verification, ensuring the integrity of the internal lubrication system. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the throttle response and hydraulic steering rack remain telepathic. A mechanically sound specimen for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
