    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW M2 in the iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been a joy to own and has been treated with the respect a performance machine deserves. The exterior paint retains a deep luster, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, light scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014all typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is a clean, non-smoker environment. The black Dakota leather seats with blue contrast stitching are in great shape, showing only slight softening of the leather on the driver's side bolster. All electronics, including the iDrive navigation and Harman Kardon premium sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has a full-service history with recent oil and brake fluid services completed. The tires have plenty of life remaining, and the engine delivers smooth, consistent power. This is a solid, honest example of a modern enthusiast car that is ready to be driven and appreciated immediately.",
